=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Overviews_Operators_ex5 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright clean sound, with saw_like oscillator character around 364 Hz, featuring punchy attack and dynamic envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally rich.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: dynamic
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: clean
  spectral_complexity_mean: rich
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 363.6388
  harmonic_decay_rate: -1.3786
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9495
  pitch_clarity: 25.5359
  inharmonicity: 0.9423
  type: saw_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -3.0516
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

